rComments: Very enthusiastic about teaching and UX. Always asking students if they require further assistance with course content and assignments, very accessible through office hours and email.

Hands down one of the best professors I have ever had. Michelle genuinely cares about her students and tries her hardest to get everyone excited about UX. She shows up to every class highly enthusiastic and well prepared. She is very accessible outside of class and responds to email fast and with thought. Great course, better prof!

decent teacher but assignments were extremely tough and sometimes impossible! did not teach us enough for us to complete our assignments successfully. would recommend taking an easier class if you can!
